                  <m>g(x) = 2x - 7(2 - x)</m>
                </p>
              </li>
              <li>
                <p>
                  <m>g(x) = 2x - 7x(2 - x)</m>
                </p>
              </li>
              <li>
                <p>
                  <m>g(x) = 2 - 7(2 - x)</m>
                </p>
              </li>
              <li>
