          </p>
          <p>
            Vertical Intercept: <m>15</m>; When you first rent the kayak,
            there is a <m>$15</m> charge.
            Or, in simpler terms, there is a flat fee charge of
            <m>$15</m> in addition to the hourly rate.
          </p>
        </solution>
