          </p>
        </statement>
        <solution>
          <p>
            Since the input variable is <m>y</m>,
            the <m>y</m>-intercept in this context is the horizontal intercept of the function which is <m>4</m> or <m>(4,0)</m>
          </p>
        </solution>
      </exercise>
